Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 吃饭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在吃了 在吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梦 那个饵料难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 不会过甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是甜的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃吧 文太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀 这家伙是只花猫 难道不是母的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是母的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就给它起一个更女孩子点的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如 加奈 呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这得取得本人的同意啊 虽然绝对不会同意的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为看嘛 这孩子一脸文静相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？代理已经出门了么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 本想一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是去久违的学校 现在正干劲十足的进行扩张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扩张？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,角鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各肠？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.31,0:00:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:00:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 已经这个点了 迟到了 迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟到了 迟到了 迟到了 迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.87,0:01:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈酱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上学的日子的早餐吃面包就可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.71,0:01:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 好的 我知道了 那么我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一来 就能在新学期看到咬着面包的少女的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.63,0:01:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟到了 迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…的画面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别大清早就开始喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆 今天是暑假中的返校日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是入住专卖所以来第一次上学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然担心会不会迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是多亏了送报的经验 甚至还发现了近路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:02:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆 我觉得我能把送报娘做好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:37.32,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(455,320)}{\fad(500,0)}第一次的、微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦 健君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 上次从健君妈妈那里得到的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在哪家店里买的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是妈妈亲手做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的么 太好吃了 我还以为是哪家有名的点心店做的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:04:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我跟妈妈说再给你做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢啦 健君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲妃酱 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说哦 我妈妈说想订咲妃酱家的报纸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真的么 那么放学之后请让我跟你妈妈谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 我也跟妈妈说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶上了 赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们听说了哦 你婆婆的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有什么我们能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管什么尽管吩咐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打铃了 大家请就座
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 一会说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 大家请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天虽然是临时上课 但要为大家介绍一位转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从第二学期开始就要在我们学校上学的久地院美华同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院 请简单介绍下自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 我和你们不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不要随随便便跟我说话 明白了么 你们这些平民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？那是什么性格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那发言行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该拿这孩子怎么办好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你啊 中町加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来只是偶然在附近见过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:06:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以比起说是熟人不如说是伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙伴？只是偶然见面就？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁跟像你这样的平民是伙伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋…朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我不需要平民做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐 久地院同学穿的校服是白蔷薇学院的制服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个超有钱人上的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是倒是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为什么呢 好不容易在白蔷薇学院上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却为什么来我们学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去在有钱人的学校上学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转到了经济实惠的都立中学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(180,30)}{\fs25}{\fad(500,500)}需要被关心…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是我们中校的校服 我们的也很好看吧 呐呐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底想说什么 把我当笨蛋么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 加奈 带她参观下校内如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦 你还完全不知道学校里面的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 我从来都不向平民打听问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈才是 要依靠我也行哦 问什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快就要问了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个无礼的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拜托买的酒可别忘了买哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 怎么样？久违的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我是个无礼的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦 意义不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈酱真是的 太可爱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动不动就发情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦 那么 就一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 又发情了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要八次 八次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回数怎么还增加啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八次都不行啊 那还有五次 再来五次就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问做什么 一直不就是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是问你这个 是问你们把门开着在搞些什么名堂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人家知道我们这有变态在 合同会减少的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 收获如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还用说 理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是代理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扩张业务辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这个「扩张」到底是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上也听到了这词
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劝诱的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劝诱？ 是订报纸的劝诱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:09:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报社还能劝诱别人订其他东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但是在小学里进行劝诱…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说 小学里的学生都是这附近的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他们搞好关系的话 从而就能跟他们的父母亲近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 要和他们签订报合同也容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做到这种地步吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是基本 基本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然加奈已经来我们这干了 就要精通完美的扩张笑容哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扩张笑容？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 仔细看好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 你试试
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要做了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼镜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这感觉该怎么说呢 好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 不应该强迫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行？ 我不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微笑 这样吗 还是这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是不行么 好奇怪 哪个地方没做对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 普通的微笑是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混沌颜 是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 多做练习的话肯定会变好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以加奈…别真哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练习啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是加奈么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 又迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才迷路了 你这个无礼的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 那是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…是那个 偶然从附近经过顺便到你这来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 有客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 这位是久地院美华同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在花日报社…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花日？ 你是花日报社的间谍？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你凭什么随意做出这种错误的论断
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奉命出来进行扩张 顺便…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说扩张？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是劝诱别人订报纸的意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然知道 比起那个 你给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院同学 稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.32,0:11:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 你给我听好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花日报纸在上个月订报时间快结束时抢走了我们15家生意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去问了理由 居然是「米」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「订他们的报纸的话 就附送大米哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又是不米店！是报社啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没米的话吃纸不就好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,综上所述 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去进行扩张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 日记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 日记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还真是偶然呢 加奈也去扩张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起偶然 其实是代理…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 你和她一起去扩张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你在她旁边微笑 明白了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 但是我的笑脸还…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个笑脸会成为强力的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强力的武器 我的笑脸不是还不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你的笑脸非常棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好的笑脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然是行的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以干劲十足的去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 那么说加奈也要跟我去同一个地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扩张原来是同别的专卖所的人一同工作的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我按咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要订花日报纸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院同学这样不行啊 这个人是外国人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 花日报纸？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能听懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:14:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我是风新报纸 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NO~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 下一家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是花日报纸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是风新报纸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要订报纸么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…久地院同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一家！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 吓跑的客人让小遥去签回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全军覆没了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样呢 久地院同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不太明白 但大家好象是看到加奈的脸后就把门关上的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是但是 代理说我的笑脸很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大家一看到我的脸就把门关了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这是为什么呢 咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 真是个喋喋不休的烦人家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看 加奈的那个笑脸让我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…我笑了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那笑脸很糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:16:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 果然很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那么变为不糟糕的笑脸不就可以了么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练习 练习笑容的话就会好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 代理也跟我说要靠练习
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那么让我帮助你练习也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过你可以依靠我的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太感谢了 美华酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美华…酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 别叫得这样轻浮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 美…久地院同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉就 哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 我觉得是非常棒的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是当然 好了 加奈也试着做做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛太眯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回睁太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底哪点没做好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不知道如何是好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是太僵硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院同学 好痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 还算可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 已经不是很糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们出阵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在家吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电表在转 肯定在家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岂有此理 看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做不行的啊 要被骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么做好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢吞吞的 既然这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,着火啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,着火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,着火？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,着火？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪着火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没地方着火 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么吓死了 让好不容易到手的机会跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练习的结果 展示加奈笑容的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 好不容易久地院同学那么努力地帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却逃跑了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么蠢话 竟然说我是为了你什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经8点了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点回去的话 大家一定要担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 从今以后叫我名也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:20:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我心胸宽广嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了 美华酱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈那个家伙 明明可以笑出那么灿烂的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说起来 我今天做了笑容的练习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑容的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练习吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的 加奈的扩张笑容真的很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了 不要哭 加奈酱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起 糟糕的是这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此我努力的练习了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让我们看看练习的成果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我要笑了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？ 我有什么不对劲的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 比起白天那个 进步了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 到底是什么样的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是变的相当不错了么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈酱 真的太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆 我和大家在一起感觉非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 第一次的、游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.34,0:23:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要玩点心的接词游戏咯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,yo 优酪乳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,to 巧克力糖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,fu 麸果子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.00,0:23:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,si 咸牛奶糖
